{
  "chapter": 47,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十七回 大欢喜女菩萨\n\n李寻欢与铃铃在归途中论\"痴\"字真意，铃铃感慨李寻欢即将离去。二人循酒菜香气回到小楼，发现楼内灯火通明、笑语喧哗。李寻欢率先登楼，惊见二十多名奇胖女子围坐进食，为首的正是大欢喜女菩萨——一位体型如肉山的女高手，身旁侍奉着五六名年轻男子。大欢喜女菩萨识破李寻欢为蓝蝎子而来，对其胆识与良心表示赞赏。她命一名紫衣男子为李寻欢倒酒，该男子竟认出李寻欢身份。大欢喜女菩萨令其展示剑法，李寻欢震惊地发现此人竟是藏剑山庄少庄主游龙生——昔日英俊少年已沦为大欢喜女菩萨的玩物。游龙生持夺情剑表演剑法，剑光如秋水。大欢喜女菩萨又令游龙生以剑刺其咽喉，游龙生突然出剑，剑光闪电般刺入——章末留悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "痴并不可笑，因为惟有至情的人，才能学得会这'痴'字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "痴也要学？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "当然，无论谁想学会这'痴'字，都不是件易事，因为'痴'和'呆'不同，只有痴于剑的人，才能练成精妙的剑法，只有痴于情的人，才能得到别人的真情，这些事，不痴的人是不会懂的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "和你在一起，我的确懂得了许多事，只可惜……只可惜你就要走了，而且绝不会带我走。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "至少我会先陪你回去。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那么，我们为何不走地道？那条路岂非近得多么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我可不是老鼠，为何要走地道？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "只有那些见不得天日的人，才喜欢走地道，一个人不到万不得已的时候，还是莫要走地道的好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，我听你的话，以后绝不做老鼠。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你看，这里有清风，有明月，还有如此清的流水，这些事，那些专走地道的人哪里能享受得到？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我倒宁愿天上挂的是月饼，地上流的是美酒……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "老实说，我肚子实在饿了，饿得要命，回去后，第一件事我就要下厨房，做几样好吃的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "炸子鸡、红烧肉、辣椒……还有极好的陈年花雕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你也闻到味道了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "年纪大了的人，耳朵虽会变得有点聋，眼睛也会变得有点花，但鼻子却还是照样灵得很的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你可嗅得出这味道是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我只知道镇上那小店绝没有这么好的酒，也做不出这么好的菜。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "何况那小店早就关门了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "也许是哪家好吃的人正在做宵夜。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "绝不会，这镇上住的几十户人家我都知道，他们日子过得都很节省，就算偶尔想弄顿宵夜吃，最多也不过煮碗面，打两个蛋而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "也许他们家有远客来了，所以特别招待……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也不会，绝没有一家的媳妇，能烧得出这么香的菜。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就是我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "所以我才奇怪，我还没有下厨房，这酒菜的香气是从哪里来的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "这酒菜的香气，就是从你那小楼上传来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "莫非是你们家的小姐已回来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "绝不会，她说过至少也要等三五个月后才会回来。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "你们家的客人本不少，也许又有远客来了，主人既不在，就自己动手弄些酒菜吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我先上去瞧瞧，你……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "还是我先上去的好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_ling",
      "speaker_name": "铃铃",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？这些人既然在楼上又烧莱，又喝酒，闹得这么厉害，显然并没有什么恶意，你难道还怕我先上去有危险不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_ling_ling",
      "text": "我只不过也很饿了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "大欢喜女菩萨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知道我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "久仰得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你却没有逃走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "我为何要逃走？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我虽还不知道你是谁，但你的来意我已知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你是为了蓝蝎子来的，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她杀死我那宝贝徒弟，就是为了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "所以你想来救她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "想不到你这男人倒还有点良心，她为你杀人，倒还不冤枉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但蓝蝎子也真可算是个了不起的女人，讲义气，有骨头，她杀了我的徒弟，非但没有逃走，反而敢来见我，以前我倒真未想到她是这么样的一个人，跟你倒可算是天生的一对儿。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "女菩萨若肯成全，在下感激不尽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你想将她带走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我若已杀了她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "那么……我也许就要替她报仇了！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，你不但有良心，也有胆子，我倒还真舍不得杀你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "去，替这位客人倒酒。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "礼貌",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，好酒量！好酒量的男人才是好男人，我这些男人谁也不比上你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "李探花千杯不醉，请，再尽这一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "李探花真是贵人多忘事，连老朋友都不认得了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "你的人他虽已不认得，你的剑法他想必还是认得的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "我的剑法……我的剑法连我自己都忘了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "你没有忘，快去拿你的剑来。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "来，露一手给他瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑法！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "夺情剑！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "游龙生，阁下莫非是'藏剑山庄'的游少庄主。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "老朋友毕竟是老朋友，你到底还是没有忘了我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "藏剑山庄的厨子做不出这么好的炸鸡来么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "他们做出来的炸鸡简直就像木头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "若不是我，你能吃到这种炸鸡么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "吃不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "你跟我在一起，日子过得开心不开心？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "开心死了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "蓝蝎子和我，若要你选一个，你选谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "当然是选我们的女菩萨。",
      "tone": "谄媚",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "好，这小子总算是有眼光的，也不枉我疼你一场！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "来，往我这地方刺一剑，给李探花瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "text": "那不行，若是伤了女菩萨，那怎么得了，我也要心疼死了。",
      "tone": "谄媚",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_huan_xi_nv_pu_sa",
      "speaker_name": "大欢喜女菩萨",
      "listener": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "text": "小兔崽子，凭你也能伤得了我，放心刺过来吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_long_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "游龙生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    }
